<section>
    <h2>Program Overview</h2>
    <p>Founded on the principles of the Word of God, ABBA’s Kingdom Donation Program reflects the Spirit of generosity, abundance, and stewardship. Through this initiative, we reveal the Father’s heart and Kingdom provision, creating opportunities for individuals to sow and reap in alignment with Heaven’s economy.</p>
</section>

<section>
    <h2>Biblical Foundation</h2>
    <p>The foundation of this program is rooted in Scripture:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><span class="highlight">Deuteronomy 14:24-26:</span> The tithe is not just for the temple but also for rejoicing and provision among God’s people.</li>
        <li><span class="highlight">Acts 2:44-45:</span> The early church shared all things in common, demonstrating the Spirit of generosity.</li>
        <li><span class="highlight">John 21:6:</span> Jesus’ blessing of abundance after the disciples had fished all night symbolizes His unchanging provision.</li>
    </ul>
</section>

<section>
    <h2>Sowing and Reaping</h2>
    <h3>Main Link Donations</h3>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>42% Co-Creator:</strong> Stewarding the vision and ongoing development of the program.</li>
        <li><strong>58% Kingdom Vision:</strong> Empowering projects and outreach to transform lives and communities.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Affiliate Link Donations</h3>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>90% Affiliate:</strong> Empowering individuals to steward resources for their own dreams.</li>
        <li><strong>9% Kingdom Vision:</strong> Supporting the overarching mission of the Kingdom.</li>
        <li><strong>1% Co-Creator:</strong> Accountability and leadership stewardship.</li>
    </ul>
</section>

<section>
    <h2>Four-Phase Plan</h2>
    <h3>Phase 1: Foundations (Months 1-3)</h3>
    <p><strong>Goal:</strong> 1,000 donors. Build momentum through trust and testimonies.</p>

    <h3>Phase 2: Regional Expansion (Months 4-12)</h3>
    <p><strong>Goal:</strong> 10,000 donors. Multiply impact with affiliate sharing and strong community engagement.</p>

    <h3>Phase 3: National Impact (Year 2-4)</h3>
    <p><strong>Goal:</strong> 100,000 donors. Partner with large ministries and organizations.</p>

    <h3>Phase 4: Global Reach (Year 5-7)</h3>
    <p><strong>Goal:</strong> 17% penetration of reachable demographics (~200M). Transform nations through Kingdom stewardship.</p>
</section>

